<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>EMA616_05_IH_0003_s</title>

  <!-- 공통 js-->
  <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
  <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

  <!-- 공통 css-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

  <!-- 개별 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
  <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema511_01.css" /> -->
  <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema616_03_05.css" /> -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema616_05.css" />
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema616_05_ih_0003 paging">
    <section class="title type2">
      <h2 data-head="3_orange" lang="y">직육면체의 부피는 몇 ㎥인지 구해 보세요.</h2>
    </section>

    <section class="contents">
      <div class="question_box justify_center">
        <div class="flex justify_center dir_col gap_40">
          <div class="box_left flex justify_center">
            <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_04_IH/616_04_03_S.png" alt="" />

            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="24" text-align="center" class="input_middle"></math-field>
              <span class="ml_12">㎥</span>
            </div>
 

            <p class="txt1">4 m</p>
            <p class="txt2">3 m</p>
            <p class="txt3">2 m</p>
          </div>

          <div class="box_right">
            <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_04_IH/616_04_03_L.png" alt="" />
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="120" text-align="center"></math-field>
              <span class="ml_12">㎥</span>
            </div>
          

            <p class="txt4">4 m</p>
            <p class="txt5">5 m</p>
            <p class="txt6">600 ㎝</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="solve_area">
        <div class="inner_solve">
          <div class="flex">
            <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
            <div class="conts_solve">
              <ul>
                <li lang="y"> 가로가 3m, 세로가 2m, 높이가 4m인 직육면체의 부피는 3&times;2&times;4=24 (㎥)입니다.</li>
                <li lang="y"> 600cm=6m이므로 가로가 5m, 세로가 6m, 높이가 4m인 직육면체의 부피는 5&times;6&times;4=120 (㎥)입니다.</li>
                <!-- <li class="tid">
                    <span class="solve_img">다른 풀이</span>
                    <p lang="y">새로 만든 직육면체의 가로는 3×3=9 (㎝), 세로는 4×3=12 (㎝), 높이는 2×3=6 (㎝)이므로 부피는 9×12×6=648 (㎤)입니다.</p>
                  </li> -->
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="btn_area">
        <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
        <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
        <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>

</html>